      "name": "Turbulence model sensitivity — k-omega SST vs. RSM comparison",
      "description": "Comparison of k-omega SST and Reynolds Stress Model predictions for shear stress distribution at nominal operating conditions. Both models applied to undegraded pump geometry. k-omega SST selected as primary model based on computational cost and agreement with experimental shear stress proxy measurements."
    }
